nodes.text: Kellimin was an individual who was a subscriber to, and commenter on, Cynabar's Droid Datalog. After having an encounter with an IT-O Interrogator, Kellimin described them as "impersonally evil things." Commenting on the entry for the droid in the Datalog in 3 BBY, Kellimin noted that their existence was reason enough to oppose the Emperor since he allowed them to be used.
